Package com.tailf.ned

Class NedShowFilter

Object
com.tailf.ned.NedShowFilter
public class NedShowFilter extends Object
Filter used when requesting data from a NED using the showStatsFilter method. Corresponds to the subtree filter in a NETCONF get or get-config request and should be handled according to RFC6241.
